to enable threat prioritization, airspace control, coordinated response, and resource management of CsUAS capabilities. Matures technical solutions to defeat sUAS
capabilities, including target acquisition, navigation, and control, in addition to identifying and exploiting weaknesses in sUAS system design and operation.

