algorithms to enable threat prioritization, airspace control, coordinated response, and resource management of C-SUAS capabilities. Mature, demonstrate, and transition
interceptor capabilities to deliver physical effects that enable faster intercept, greater standoff ranges, increased magazine depth, survivability, affordability, and/or
decrease in size, weight, and/or power requirements.

