A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Project matures and demonstrates a mission systems architecture to support Future Vertical Lift (FVL) through utilization of a reconfigurable and flexible tiered
architectural approach.

 Work in this Project is fully coordinated with Program Element (PE) 0602148A (Future Vertical Lift Technology).

 The cited work is consistent with the Under Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering Science and Technology focus areas and the Army Modernization
 Strategy.

 Work in this Project is performed by the Aviation & Missile Center (AvMC).

