A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Program Element (PE) supports component development and prototyping for organizational equipment, improved individual clothing and equipment that enhance
Soldier battlefield effectiveness, survivability, and sustainment. This PE also supports the component development and prototyping of joint service food and combat
feeding equipment designed to reduce logistics burden.

