defense. The SW factory will continue to maintain a DevSecOps infrastructure and ecosystem (to include
embedded M&S and test capabilities) to necessary to develop and deliver code at a faster pace than currently
feasible. Test architected software on MK 6 Mod X hardware and deliver to test sites.
