FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2027 funding Increased compared to FY 2026 by 4.910 million due to the transfer of the Directed Energy Bioeffects effort and
associated funding within this Program Element from Project 635323 / Directed Energy Bioeffects Parameters to Project 635323/
Human Effectiveness Technology Demonstration. However, the overall funding for the Directed Energy Bioeffects effort increased
