accurately evaluating the credibility of Publicly Available Information (PAI) from various modalities (audio, video, text, and Internet
of Things (IoT) devices), and integrating with traditional intelligence, surveillance, and reconnaissance (ISR) sources, focusing on
developing and refining algorithms for the fusion and clustering of multi-source data, and methods of verification.
